Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:13.34,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.15,0:00:15.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:19.08,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.37,0:00:23.04,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:26.67,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:30.42,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:33.63,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:36.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:40.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:44.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.98,0:00:48.61,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.61,0:00:51.28,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:54.78,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:59.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:02.83,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.63,0:01:11.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:13.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:15.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:18.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.93,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs125\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,160.389)}The Monstrous Doctor Insect
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.93,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,690.389)}and the Shocker School
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:30.67,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&}Catch rhinoceros beetles\Nwith {\c&H1011C3&}Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.67,0:01:33.85,Italics,,0,0,0,,Attention, sweet children\Nof the amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.85,0:01:34.94,Italics,,0,0,0,,Good day to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:39.62,Italics,,0,0,0,,I have some big news,\Nif you'll please gather around.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.15,0:01:44.68,Italics,,0,0,0,,If you want to hunt rhino\Nbeetles with Kamen Rider,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.68,0:01:47.17,Italics,,0,0,0,,please get on this bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.66,0:01:49.46,Italics,,0,0,0,,Just get on the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We get to hunt rhino\Nbeetles with Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm more interested in Kamen\NRider than the beetles!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.25,0:01:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's hunt rhino\Nbeetles with Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.70,0:02:00.12,Italics,,0,0,0,,Get on, get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:01.80,Italics,,0,0,0,,No pushing, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.53,0:02:03.76,Italics,,0,0,0,,In order!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:05.33,Italics,,0,0,0,,That's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.26,0:02:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.62,0:02:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.42,0:02:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has\Nhis trusty Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.48,0:02:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll catch up with the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.42,0:02:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider's coming through!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.57,0:02:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there foul work afoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going after Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to hunt rhino beetles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.29,0:02:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Rhino beetles?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone went to go hunt rhino\Nbeetles with Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.60,0:03:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say hunt beetles\Nwith the Kamen Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So who took them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.42,0:03:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shucks, it's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.01,0:03:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs60\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H1011C3&}Mount Takao Cable Car
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's Mount Takao.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.33,0:03:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NWe're on Mount Takao.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.03,0:03:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also called\NRhino Beetle Mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the Kamen Rider is\Nsomewhere on this mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.38,0:03:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Go find him, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.46,0:03:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Kamen Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see Kamen\NRider anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Not one rhino beetle, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.89,0:03:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Maybe we should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom's probably worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! It's a rhino beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty big, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's big!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a rhino beetle monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.07,0:04:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run away, children!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to be\Nstudents of Shocker School!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I will now educate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.94,0:04:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the insect\Ndoctor Kabutrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Greet your teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Doctor Insect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.96,0:04:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,One,\Nour enemy is the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:05:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We've recruited a fine bunch of\Nstudents for our Shocker School.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I used both the Kamen Rider\Nand rhinoceros beetles as bait
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and they came right along with\Nme, Ambassador Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we produce the Shocker\NSchool's first graduating class,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll create Shocker\NSchools all over the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and really shock the adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If we make sure all the children\Nwho inherit the world after them
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.74,0:05:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,are all members of Shocker,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,then the world will easily\Nfall into Shocker's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they\Nweren't abducted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:57.45,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an9\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&}Catch rhinoceros beetles\Nwith {\c&H1011C3&}Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:06:00.21,Italics,,0,0,0,,Make sure you do as I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Doctor Insect!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to follow\Nthat microbus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to talk to one\Nof the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.94,0:06:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.86,0:06:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Saki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you meet Kamen Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you catch any rhino beetles?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.99,0:06:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never playing with you\Nagain, Koichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.66,0:06:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's mean! Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.77,0:06:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't leave until you tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Or I'll make you pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you pretend to be the Kamen\NRider, that means you're our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Saki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Insect will\Npraise us for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.46,0:06:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:06:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you kids doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:07:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, Koichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Kamen Rider can't go\Ncrying when he's on his Cyclone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Saki and the others said\NKamen Rider was an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.75,0:07:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they'd kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They really said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.07,0:07:20.29,Italics,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Shocker is planning\Nsomething with the children...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.12,0:07:32.14,Italics,,0,0,0,,School bus. School bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:34.17,Italics,,0,0,0,,You're being tailed. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't shake me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.57,0:08:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You sped up when you\Nrealized I was on your tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't done anything,\Nyou wouldn't have tried to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.79,0:08:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Acting on orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds like a\Nconfession to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's giving the orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.73,0:08:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The iron man of\NShocker, Kabutrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:53.13,Italics,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:00.69,Italics,,0,0,0,,Show yourself, Kabutrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Open that door!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.68,Italics,,0,0,0,,You come in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kabutrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.01,0:09:21.22,Italics,,0,0,0,,Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:25.82,Italics,,0,0,0,,The Shocker School\Nbus cannot be escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:28.61,Italics,,0,0,0,,You're not capable of\Nbreaking out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:30.94,Italics,,0,0,0,,Now I'll send you to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.98,0:09:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not working!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:42.96,Italics,,0,0,0,,Your struggle is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:49.05,Italics,,0,0,0,,The bus' frame and windows are strong\Nenough to resist a blast from a bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a train coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If even a bazooka won't dent it...\Nthe bus is as tough as a tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If the train hits it,\Nit will be a catastrophe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.81,0:10:17.34,Italics,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.27,0:10:21.28,Italics,,0,0,0,,You hear the train\Ncoming, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:29.65,Italics,,0,0,0,,You claim to fight for peace, yet you're\Nabout to become a terrible killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.19,0:10:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, the train is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave them to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're almost there!\NKeep going, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.78,0:11:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's pushing\Nfrom the other side!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.23,0:11:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:48.62,Bumper Episode 53-69,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\pos(280,94)\c&H05008E&}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see who'll win...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.55,0:11:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the iron man Kabutrong,\Nor the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:11:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, Kabutrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.53,0:12:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost had you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kabutrong... what are you\Ngathering those children together for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,For education...\Nas the first class of the Shocker School.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker School?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In time, we'll build Shocker\NSchools all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, all the world's children\Nwill become Shocker's pupils!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:13:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And would you be their\Nteacher, Kabutrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me\Nlaugh, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't stand a chance against\Nthe mighty cyborg Kabutrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay, Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.24,0:14:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make a move, or Taki dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.35,0:14:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, this goes\Nhere, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.79,0:14:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki's the one who...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Mr. Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:14:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.36,0:15:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- Shocker? \N- Is this true, Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we use Taki as\Nmaterial for the Shocker School?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shocker School?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll use him for the first\Nclass' graduation exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Administer the graduation\Nexam tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:23.85,Italics,,0,0,0,,First class of Shocker School!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:26.42,Italics,,0,0,0,,Doctor Insect orders you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:28.81,Italics,,0,0,0,,Assemble tomorrow\Nat eight o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.81,0:15:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Doctor. We'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a transmitter...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki's fate depends on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:15:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.03,0:16:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How far are they taking us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope this transmitter works...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, 20 degrees,\N20 minutes to the northeast.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.92,0:16:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Still driving down the\NKoshu Kaido towards Otsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.66,0:16:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Goro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Koshu Kaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shocker School bus Goro\Nis on is headed for Mount Takao.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mount Takao?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course...\Nthat's where Shocker's base is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.99,0:17:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, I'll join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's taking them so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We will now commence the\NShocker School graduation exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Students of Shocker School.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The rhino beetles I gave you are\Nwonderful weapons, miniature grenades.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:18:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, throw them at this man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gonna kill Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The brat who defies Shocker, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make you part\Nof the test as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Takeshi and the\NKamen Rider are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider has already lost\Nto the great Kabutrong once!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.90,0:18:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The next time he faces\Nme, he dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.39,0:18:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so sure, Kabutrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.09,0:18:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.27,0:18:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Rider!\N- Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.48,0:18:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No use... it's a dead end!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.11,0:21:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's finish this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.17,0:21:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.54,0:22:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.24,0:22:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.48,0:22:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all sound asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.15,0:22:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,With Kabutrong gone,\Nthe children should be back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.90,0:22:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a close call, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.67,0:22:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But thanks to the three of you,\Nthe Shocker School is closed for business.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.95,0:22:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.75,0:22:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get the kids to safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.18,0:22:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.94,0:22:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.55,0:22:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye! Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.72,0:22:58.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider has put an\Nend to the Shocker School.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.70,0:23:02.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Shocker would find a\Nnew target soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:04.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Keep fighting, Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.70,0:23:07.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.09,0:23:10.68,Cont,,0,50,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:13.60,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(290.175,252.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.49,0:23:14.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin\Nsent by Shocker HQ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:15.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous Kamikirikid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.34,0:23:18.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Flames crackle and burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.16,0:23:20.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell chants\Nan eerie magic spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.18,0:23:24.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What is the terrible Shocker ritual\Nthat uses Kamen Rider as a sacrifice?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.80,0:23:29.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for "The Shocker\NGraveyard: Monsters Revived."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.53,0:23:31.00,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fs115\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,725.389)}The Shocker Graveyard:\NMonsters Revived
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:40.85,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.44,0:23:43.44,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.44,0:23:45.40,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.40,0:23:48.44,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:50.82,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.82,0:23:52.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.70,0:23:54.49,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.49,0:23:55.91,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.20,0:23:58.33,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.37,0:24:04.08,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.08,0:24:07.63,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.63,0:24:11.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.72,0:24:15.55,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The Monstrous Doctor Insect\Nand the Shocker School
Comment: 0,0:23:27.53,0:23:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shocker Graveyard:\NMonsters Revived